OL,3,CNew Lord of The Rings film co-written
OL,4,Cby Stephen Colbert announced
OL,6,FA new Lord of The Rings movie has been
OL,7,Fannounced by Warner Bros, which will
OL,8,Fbe co-written by comedian and
OL,9,Ftelevision host Stephen Colbert.
OL,11,FThe film, which reportedly has a
OL,12,Fworking title of Lord of the Rings:
OL,13,FShadow of the Past, is in development
OL,14,Falongside The Hunt for Gollum, which
OL,15,Fis already set to be released next
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,18,FLord of The Rings Director Peter
OL,19,FJackson made the announcement in a
OL,20,Fvideo posted on X "in honor of Tolkien
OL,21,FReading Day".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
