OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774458668
OL,3,CNew Lord of The Rings film co-written
OL,4,Cby Stephen Colbert announced
OL,6,FIn the clip, Jackson introduces
OL,7,FColbert as a "very special partner",
OL,8,Fwho will assist in producing the new
OL,9,Ffilm.
OL,11,FAppearing via video link, Colbert, who
OL,12,Fis an avid and lifelong Tolkien fan,
OL,13,Fsaid he was "pretty happy" about being
OL,14,Finvolved.
OL,16,FThe film is set 14 years after Frodo's
OL,17,Fpassing, and will follow his close
OL,18,Fcompanions Sam, Merry, and Pippin as
OL,19,Fthey set out to retrace the first
OL,20,Fsteps of their adventure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
