FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774458668
OL,3,CNew Lord of The Rings film co-written
OL,4,Cby Stephen Colbert announced
OL,6,FThe comedian revealed a little of the
OL,7,Ffilm's premise, saying: "The thing I
OL,8,Ffound myself reading over and over
OL,9,Fagain were the six chapters early on
OL,10,Fthe fellowship" that were "never
OL,11,Fdeveloped into the first movie".
OL,13,FColbert explained that he felt this
OL,14,Fpart of the original book could "be
OL,15,Fits own story that could fit into the
OL,16,Flarger story".
OL,18,FHe added that he wants the new film to
OL,19,Fbe "completely faithful to the books,
OL,20,Fwhilst also being completely faithful
OL,21,Fto the movies" already made.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
