OL,3,CNew Lord of The Rings film co-written
OL,4,Cby Stephen Colbert announced
OL,6,FThe Lord of the Rings franchise, based
OL,7,Fon the writing of JRR Tolkien, is a
OL,8,Fglobal cultural phenomenon.
OL,10,FThe final film in the original live-
OL,11,Faction trilogy, The Lord of the Rings:
OL,12,FThe Return of the King, won all 11
OL,13,FOscars for which it was nominated in
OL,14,F2003.
OL,16,FSince then, there have been several
OL,17,Fspin-offs and a sequel trilogy based
OL,18,Fon Tolkien's novel, The Hobbit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
