OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774458668
OL,3,CNew Lord of The Rings film co-written
OL,4,Cby Stephen Colbert announced
OL,6,FColbert worked on the idea for the new
OL,7,Ffilm for several years alongside his
OL,8,Fscreenwriter son Peter McGee, before
OL,9,F"scraping (his) courage into a pile"
OL,10,Fand calling director Jackson.
OL,12,FThe TV personality, who previously had
OL,13,Fa cameo in The Hobbit: The Desolation
OL,14,Fof Smaug alongside his family, will be
OL,15,Fwriting alongside his son and
OL,16,Ffranchise veteran Philippa Boyens.
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
