OL,3,CNew Lord of The Rings film co-written
OL,4,Cby Stephen Colbert announced
OL,6,FIn July last year CBS announced that
OL,7,FThe Late Show with Stephen Colbert
OL,8,Fwould end in spring 2026 after 33
OL,9,Fyears on air.
OL,11,FThe television network said at the
OL,12,Ftime that the move was "purely a
OL,13,Ffinancial decision against a
OL,14,Fchallenging backdrop in late night
OL,15,F(television)" and "not related in any
OL,16,Fway to the show's performance, content
OL,17,For other matters."
OL,26,@wD@ApmwD@Lpn
