OL,3,CNew Lord of The Rings film co-written
OL,4,Cby Stephen Colbert announced
OL,6,FWhen asked by Jackson if Colbert was
OL,7,F"sure he had the time" to work on the
OL,8,Fnew film, Colbert joked: "It turns out
OL,9,Fthat I'm going to be free starting
OL,10,Fthis summer".
OL,12,FThere is currently no release date for
OL,13,Fthe film.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
